<P>
MOTION IN LIMINE WINS GUSHER 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
LOUISVILLE, Ky. 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Motion In Limine overhauled-Dynawite in the final furlong and went on to a 
two-length victory in Tuesday's $29,425 The Gusher purse at Churchill Downs. 
</P>
<P>
The winner, under Dean Kutz, covered the mile in 1:37 3/5 and paid $8.60. 
Fashion White finished second with Dynawite third, another half length back. 
</P>
