<P>
Georgians Cancel Tour: The Georgian State Dance Company, now performing in New 
York though Sunday, has canceled its nine-city tour -- including a 
seven-performance run at the Pantages which was to begin next Wednesday -- 
because of disappointing ticket sales. Anne Abrams, the Los Angeles 
spokeswoman, said ticket sales were "not even moderate." CLAUDIA PUIG 
</P>
