</P>
</TYPE>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
ENTREPRENEURS; VENTURE CAPITAL; COLLEGE COURSES; UNIVERSITY OF CALIFORNIA AT 
IRVINE 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA103190-0125 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 300773 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
October 31, 1990, Wednesday, Orange County Edition 
